<section>
<title>Description détaillée</title>

<para>An exception thrown by SassScript.</para>

<para>This class does not implement SassException on purpose, as it should never be returned to the outside code. The compilation will catch it and replace it with a SassException reporting the location of the error. </para>
</section>
